  "prompt": "What is the most used word in Malayalam?",
  "response": "The most frequently used word in Malayalam, like many languages, is likely to be a common function word, such as articles, prepositions, or pronouns. In many languages, words like \"the,\" \"is,\" \"and,\" or their equivalents in other languages usually top the list. In Malayalam, words like \"\u0d06\u0d23\u0d4d\" (\u0101\u1e47u) meaning \"is\" or \"\u0d0e\u0d28\u0d4d\u0d28\" (enna) meaning \"that\" may be among the most commonly used. The exact ranking can vary based on the context and corpus analyzed.",
